{"article_id":"HCuMBvRARiTc4LRf","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Senate Majority Leader Harry Reid said Tuesday","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"he hopes to have a bill","depth":9},{"id":2,"text":"to address gun violence","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"on the Senate floor","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"soon after the Easter break ,","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"but confirmed","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"that measure will not include the assault weapons ban .","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"Sen. Dianne Feinstein , D-Calif. , told reporters Tuesday","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"she is disappointed","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"that her assault weapons ban will not be part of a larger bill ,","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"but acknowledged","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"it will likely make it easier to pass gun-related legislation through the Senate .","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"Feinstein said","depth":5},{"id":13,"text":"Reid told her Monday afternoon","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"that the ban on certain types of military-style assault weapons and high-capacity magazines would not be part of package of bills","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"that would make up the Senate legislation .","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"Reid , D-Nev. , said","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"Feinstein 's measure simply did not have the support","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"necessary to clear the floor","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"and could not pass the 60-vote threshold","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"needed","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"in order to be considered by the full Senate .","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"`` Right now , her amendment ,","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"using the most optimistic numbers ,","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"has less than 40 votes .","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"That 's not 60 , ''","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"he told reporters .","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"`` I have to get something on the floor","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"so we can have votes on that issue and the other issues . ''","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"The Senate Judiciary Committee passed three other measures , in addition to the assault weapons ban , over the past two weeks","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"that are expected to be considered in some form on the Senate floor .","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"These measures include bills","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"to strengthen federal penalties for trafficking and straw purchases ,","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"improve school safety","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"and require background checks for nearly every firearm purchase .","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"Feinstein 's ban will be voted on as an amendment to the larger package .","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"`` Obviously , I 'm disappointed ,","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"because","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"if was in the package ,","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"it would take 60 votes","depth":13},{"id":40,"text":"to get it out .","depth":13},{"id":41,"text":"You know ,","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"the enemies on this are very powerful .","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"I 've known that all my life , ''","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"she said .","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"As an amendment , it will require a majority of Senators to vote","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"to add it to the bill .","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"Feinstein reintroduced the ban in January as a response to the mass shooting of 20 children and six adults at an elementary school Dec. 14 in Newtown , Conn .","depth":5},{"id":48,"text":"While acknowledging her own bill would face an uphill climb as an amendment ,","depth":5},{"id":49,"text":"she held out hope","depth":6},{"id":50,"text":"that a proposal by Sen. Frank Lautenberg , D-N.J. ,","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"to ban high-capacity magazines","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"could be voted on as a separate amendment to the bill .","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"Even if the full Senate legislation does get through ,","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"Feinstein said ,","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"the fight is far from over .","depth":6},{"id":56,"text":"`` Then we face the wonderful House of Representatives , ''","depth":6},{"id":57,"text":"she said in a sarcastic reference to the Republican-controlled chamber .","depth":6},{"id":58,"text":"It was unclear when the full package of bills will be released ,","depth":3},{"id":59,"text":"but they are expected to be voted on as early as April .","depth":3},{"id":60,"text":"Asked Tuesday about the progress on the gun issue in the House ,","depth":4},{"id":61,"text":"Judiciary Chairman Bob Goodlatte , R-Va. , said ,","depth":5},{"id":62,"text":"`` There 's nothing new on that front right now . '' `` We are hard at work","depth":7},{"id":63,"text":"looking at enforcement of current gun-control laws ,","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"but we are really focused on immigration right now , ''","depth":6},{"id":65,"text":"he said .","depth":3}],"relations":[{"parent":131,"left":123,"right":130,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":123,"left":94,"right":122,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":94,"left":77,"right":93,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":77,"left":72,"right":76,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":72,"left":70,"right":71,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":70,"left":0,"right":69,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":69,"left":68,"right":4,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":68,"left":67,"right":3,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":67,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":71,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":76,"left":74,"right":75,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":74,"left":7,"right":73,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":73,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":75,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":93,"left":80,"right":92,"r